      "post_id" : 23555441,
      "comment_id" : 110247535,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Coming back to my answer 6 years later and I still like this. <b>But</b> be careful with <code>BooleanUtils.isFalse( bool )</code>. When <code>bool</code> is <code>null</code> it will return <code>false</code>, which may not be what you were expecting."
